div3.p:
Sowed the Orchard field with Smooth Mediterranean Wheat. Sowed on it 7 3/4 bushels;
       procured of Mr
       Wm J. Gilkeson at $1.12 1/2 per Bushel.

Mrs
       McF. & I dined at Mr Bumgarner's & went on to Mrs Sprouls;
       & spent the night there.

Wrote to Dr. Wm. Brown &
       remitted by Check $91.30 to pay for printing & distributing the Minutes of Synod;
       also included in the Check $3. from Mrs Cornelia Smith for Dr. Hoge's Mission.
